# n8n MCP Usage

- The available n8n MCP server is `user-n8n-mcp`.
- For now, only use the `search_nodes` tool from that MCP server.
- Do not rely on other n8n MCP tools unless the user explicitly expands the allowed scope later.
- Use `search_nodes` to look up candidate nodes and examples before building unfamiliar n8n steps.
